      "content": "objective: Select the stronger SD-WAN vendor (Fortinet vs Cisco) for a public-sector OT WAN transformation that builds a secure SD-WAN overlay and a resilient Hybrid-WAN across OT Edge, private DCs, and cloud over a 5-year horizon.\nrecommendation: Select Fortinet for controlled implementation (selected_vendor=Fortinet, score=74.6)."

